{"tid":2178241,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"張建宗：有專家呼籲市民不用參與社區檢測 屬不能接受","createTime":"2020-08-28T09:06:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T11:05:43.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"26b0e7c7da5a2276c432789b799a78a9306d159d","tid":2178241,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:06:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/rthk_new_c/129658\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frthk_new_c%2F129658&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyGhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=968bd88d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/rthk_new_c/129658</a><br />\n<br />\n政務司司長張建宗表示，政府一向重視專家意見，但他表示有專家呼籲市民不用參與普及社區檢測，屬不能接受。在立法會內會特別會議，公民黨議員郭家麒表示，醫學專家提出意見，就被冠上反中央的罪名，最終要噤聲。工聯會麥美娟表示，社會有人為政治經濟利益，抹黑檢測計劃，甚至有醫生表明因為不會受感染而不檢測，認為政府應該理直氣壯駁斥。張建宗說，抗疫期間不能以政治凌駕公共衞生，政府一向尊重及重視專家意見，亦會不遺餘力宣傳檢測計劃。會上最少兩度有議員要求張建宗，為政府引發第三波疫情導致多人死亡而道歉，張建宗未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n2020-08-28 17:02:17"},{"pid":"413ada96c65dc4fb2c6cb7d0e4bcb107eb3f904d","tid":2178241,"uid":14211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:06:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fe1c52a3efbe344c19e857084f30e43155282ff","tid":2178241,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:06:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b4c2fe9633a712850154eba13888c3ba2b0b608","tid":2178241,"uid":22556,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:07:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QHCnbYE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQHCnbYE.jpg&h=27f5eb22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我聽世衛講咋"},{"pid":"02057e03fbbb18aece841f1ff1e2762564e84b64","tid":2178241,"uid":90601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:08:04.000Z","msg":"抗疫期間不能以政治凌駕公共衞生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家正正就係政府話鳩人地唔檢疫就係反中wor大佬"},{"pid":"01718025416c7c5fff0df2251aac91c3ee34e2ef","tid":2178241,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:08:14.000Z","msg":"用党安法拉人囉咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ef7ad7b428bab31754aafac450e16226f0a91a","tid":2178241,"uid":63838,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:08:21.000Z","msg":"比低你十幾級嘅黑警散仔屌又接受到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa46739ab173248e76737b3f7752c3efda87ba5","tid":2178241,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3b4c2fe9633a712850154eba13888c3ba2b0b608","tid":2178241,"uid":22556,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:07:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QHCnbYE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQHCnbYE.jpg&h=27f5eb22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我聽世衛講咋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:08:46.000Z","msg":"世衛=親支<br />\n反世衛=反支=犯國安法?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fe3fff0683f6209ae5c9a39fe30f1281a0c90dd","tid":2178241,"uid":11291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:09:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rZUHWq1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrZUHWq1.jpg&h=504e5e95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"951d2c52c5950dd02651576a6e